(42, '<img src="uploads/rajnish/articlePic/2015-01-11_04:21:40pm_intel stick.jpeg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/>  <br/> <s>Intel has announced a small device that is slightly larger than a thumb-drive which has the capability to transform your display into a full fledged PC. You can get the device with Windows 8.1, 32GB of storage and 2GB RAM. There is also a Linux model which will come with lower memory and storage options. <br/> <s>The device is a great companion for people who want a simple and hassle free solution for their everyday computing needs or maybe for the ones who are always on the move. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Specification: <br/> <s> <s> <s>CPU: Intel Atom Processor Z3735F <br/> <s> <s> <s>PMIC: Dollar Cove AXP288 <br/> <s> <s> <s>Memory: 2GB DDR3L <br/> <s> <s> <s>Storage: eMMC 16GB/32GB/64GB <br/> <s> <s> <s>Expandable Storage: Micro SD Card Slot <br/> <s> <s> <s>Display: HDMI (Male connector) <br/> <s> <s> <s>Wifi: IEEE 802. 11 bgn <br/> <s> <s> <s>Bluetooth: Bluetooth 4.0 HS uART (Singel Wifi/Bluetooth combo chip) <br/> <s> <s> <s>Antenna: 30mm x 6.5mm x 2 mm, U shape dipole antenna <br/> <s> <s> <s>USB: USB2.0 cut type A x 1 <br/> <s> <s> <s>Power Input: Micro-USB 2.0 B connector <br/> <s> <s> <s>Power Button: Yes <br/> <s> <s> <s>Adaptor: 10W(5V/2A) <br/> <s> <s> <s>BIOS: 2MB <br/> <s> <s> <s>LED Indication: Power Status Indicator <br/> <s> <s> <s>OS: Windows (Win 8.1 with Bing, 32bit) <br/> <s> <s> <s>Asscessory: 20cm HDMI cable (optional) <br/> <s> <s> <s>Dimension: 110.9mm x 38mm x <s>9.8 mm (HDMI connector inlcuded) <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Summary: <br/> <s> <s> <s>Tiny compute stick that runs Windows 8.1, highly mobile and works with HDMI screens anywhere. <br/> <s> <s> <s>Input via standard USB, BT KB/mouse or smart device (smartphone, tablet) input via Wifi. <br/> <s> <s> <s>Highly mobile compute stick that runs Windows 8. <br/> <s> <s> <s>Transform a normal TV to a smart TV <br/> <s> <s> <s>Transform a normal Display to a computer <br/> <s> <s> <s>compute stick for homes, office, manufacturing lines or any business environment <br/> <s> <s> <s>Great device for Education and Emerging markets <br/> <s> <s> <s>Solution for mobile employees â€“ only need public monitors in the office. <br/> <s> <s> <s>Great security and cost saving on office space and compute device for mobile employees <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Availability <br/> <s>Intel expects to begin shipping the Compute Stick in Q1 of 2015, priced at $149 for the model with 2GB RAM, 32GB eMMC flash, and Windows 8.1 preinstalled, and at $89 for the Linux model with 1GB RAM, 8GB eMMC flash, and Ubuntu Linux preinstalled. <s><br/> <s>For more details check at http://goo.gl/UYU8SK.'),
(43, '<img src="uploads/mridula/challengePic/2015-01-12_09:12:03am_vivekananda_article_inner.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/>  <br/> <s>As being an youth its our responsibility to empower youth of our country. Lets raise our hands this year on YOUTH DAY (12th JAN) to empower youth. <s><br/> <s>Lets make some promises to empower youth, Being busy as like society growing, only few have time with whole day/month/life to work as social activist and empowering. <s> <br/> <s>1. Everyone should have their Youth Icon. Still if you don<r>t have choose your youth icon. <br/> <s>2. Whenever going for home or weekend do have gathering of youth and make plans. <br/> <s>3. Make discussion about trends/technology/others that will help to empower youth. <br/> <s>4. Join atleast one social activist network, NGO and keep in contact. <br/> <s>5. Start campaign with social network or join campaign on your free time. <br/> <s>6. Spread out knowledge of Life skills, health education, career guidance, english programs for rural areas etc. <br/> <s>So many other promises you can do more, search out and be connected at : http://collap.com/project.php?project_id=13 <br/> <s> <br/> <s>So, accept the challenge to change/empower youth as well as empower society. <br/> <s> <s> <s><br/> <s>In submission give your choices through which you are going to help society. <br/> <s> <s> 1. Your Youth Icon, <br/> <s> <s> 2. Area/ Region of work, <br/> <s> <s> 3. Connected NGO/social activist network, <br/> <s> <s> 4. Your plan/strategies to empower, <br/> <s> <s> 5. One best campaign picture. <s><br/> <s> <br/> <s>Arise! Awake! And stop not till the goal is reached. <br/> <s>To be good and to do good-that is the whole of religion. <br/> <s>Great undertakings are always fraught with many obstacles.'),
(44, '<img src="uploads/neeraj/articlePic/2015-01-12_02:17:20pm_Win.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/> Microsoft<r>s popular Windows 7 computer operating platform is to exit the mainstream support phase and enter the extended support stage in January 2015. <s><br/> <s>Â  <s><br/> <s>Â The Redmond-based company will port the existing Windows 7 users to the operating system<r>s extended support phase starting 13 January 2015, along with transferring the Exchange Server 2010 Enterprise and Standard editions, to extended support stage. <s><br/> <s>Â Key Windows 7 pointers you need to keep in mind: <s><br/> <s>Â  <s><br/> <s>Â 1.Mainstream support: This phase generally lasts for five years from the date of launch of any of Microsoft<r>s PC operating systems. During this period, the company will provide security fixes free of cost, along with updates (including hotfix). <s><br/> <s>Â 2. The above aspects ensure that your Windows 7 version is up to date, and has received the latest fixes for known issues. <s><br/> <s>Â 3. Extended support: Any OS that reaches the end of mainstream support, then moves to Microsoft<r>s extended support phase wherein Microsoft will not accept design-change requests or provide new features that are raised by developers. <s><br/> <s>Â 4. End of support phase: After extended support stage, which also lasts for five years, an OS will reach the end of support stage where security fixes/updates are not provided by Microsoft. <s><br/> <s>Â 5. Windows XP is a classic example of a system that reached this phase on 31 April 2014. <s><br/> <s>Â 6. Windows 7 is slated to reach end of support stage on 14 January 2020. <s><br/> <s>Â  <s><br/> <s>Â So, For know if you are asking will my Windows 7 run normally during extended support phase? <s><br/> <s>Â  <s><br/> <s>Â Yes, your OS will function normally. You will also receive updates to known issues. However, the OS will not receive new features developed by Microsoft/third-party developers.'),
(45, '<img src="uploads/rahul/projectPic/2015-01-12_03:27:35pm_Screenshot from 2015-01-12 20:50:15.png.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/> Based on widely population of web most of the people depends on the web to search any kind of data. Searching for the people on web is most desired task in present generation of the world. But when people querying particular name on search engine it will give results but it has lot of different <s><br/> <s>namesakes user feel ambiguity when selecting the particular person to decide which person user want to know and it takes much time to search particular person. In order to solve this problem we introduced the Web people search. This project describes about what is WePS, how WePS <br/> <s>will works for querying by the people, what are the different steps to disambiguate the different namesakes, what is procedure for obtaining the results in WePS. The web people search engine after searching the name it will cluster the names based on name entity so that user can easily disambiguate to identifying the particular person. In this project we try to avoid the dominance of the person name by introducing the WePS. It also reduces the user time to select desired person.'),
(46, 'The Search engine give the results based on user query key word in this the clustering is done based on the user query key word only. So that it leads to ambiguity of the namesakes and user took large time to search desired person among the all pages provide by the search engine. In order to avoid this drawback we Introduces the Web people search in this search the searching is performed based on the user queried input <s><br/> <s>Â but clustering is based on the name entities. Here name entity is the word which frequently appeared in the web page based on this we performs the clusters. In this WePS we can reduce the number of pages and the user time based on this cluster. In WePS first user gives the query on the search engine after that the system searches <s><br/> <s>Â the top K web pages K= d 1 , d 2 , d 3 ..... (d 1 , d 2 , d 3 are web pages). Â  <br/> <s>Â  <s><br/> <s>Â Now we have to perform preprocessing web pages, clustering and post processing the web pages and finally results are based on name entities. For example the user searches for the name Johnson the System first collects web pages related to the Johnson after that it will preprocesses that web pages in that preprocess step includes the Extraction, Segmentation and Name entity filtering. In the extraction the system extract the data <s><br/> <s>Â related to the name like name entity, city name, e-mail id etc. after that if one page refers multiple name sacks it will perform segmentation to split into different web pages after that perform the filtering the web pages based on the name entities and finally result will be produced Johnson farmer, Johnson sportsman, Johnson politician <s><br/> <s>Â likewise the cluster web pages will display on screen so that the user selects the desired person without ambiguity so that user searching time also reduced. Bill Gates who is not founder of Microsoft <s><br/> <s>Â this query is very difficult to search in the search engine because most of the pages <s><br/> <s>Â irrelevant to that particular person. <s><br/> <s>Â  <s><br/> <s>Â In order to solve these kinds of problems the Web People Search is introduced in this web people search it will return the cluster of pages for each individual name Bill Gate like Bill Gate politician, Bill Gate Microsoft founder and Bill Gate sport star so that user can easily identified which Bill Gate he want know. This task is quite simple for the user to search for the particular person in the web. For this purpose Web People Search uses the ER techniques the direct application of Entity Relationship techniques is that extract the extra information regarding like the name entities, n-grams and hyperlinks etc. In order to applying those ER techniques in practical there are some problems those are lake of information for each every person details to overcome these problems we consider some external resources like Wikipedia etc. One of the most powerful external resources is web only but the problem is how and what is the systematic procedure to obtaining the useful data from web. The search engine return pages referred as contextual entities and then define the inter relationships among the contextual entities in terms of web co-occurrence statistics these co-occurrence features are combined with the specialized approach that is skyline based approach. In this skyline based approach is used for deriving the external feature based similarities and the main purpose is entity resolution by considering the dominance that exists in co-occurrences of data. Now a dayâ€™s daily the Google search handle the ten million queries per day among those 5-10% queries based on web people search only. In web people search the users are searching for the particular person web pages surprisingly the latest search engines like Google, Yahoo and Bingo search <s><br/> <s>Â engines also gives the cluster of web pages regarding the that particular person. In that cluster of web pages not only having the information regarding to that querying person but also having different namesakes of information but user need to search his interesting person among that cluster of web pages this leads to the user ambiguity and it takes much time to search desired person among that cluster of web pages. Sometimes dominance problem also comes for example if people search for Bill Gates then most of the pages contains the information about the Bill gates who is the founder of Micro Soft in that case searching for person by name. <br/> <s><br/> The skyline based approach is for quality improvement over the all classification like decision tree classification etc the result of the skyline based classification aggregated with direct feature similarities which are helpful in the computing of the overall similarities of the web page pairs our <br/> approach is to increase the more direct features to increasing the overall similarity. If there are limited information about the particular web page then it performs the direct and indirect features in the clustering to improve quality of the clustering. '),
(47, 'The one of the most recently approach for web people search is exploiting querying for web people search in WePS-2 the over view of this existing solution is as follow. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>1. User input: The user types query on the Web People Search system to search about the particular person. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>2. Top K retrieval: The system sends this information to the search engine and searches the information about the query and finally retrieves top K web pages. This step is done by the most of the search engines. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>3. Pre processing: The preprocessing is performed on the top k web pages the preprocessing steps are as follows. <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> a).Extraction: The extraction is performed on the top K web pages this extraction is based on the name entity, location and hyperlink in order to extract these entities based on the existing extracting third party software. <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> b).Segmentation: If any web page refers the multiple namesakes then that web page will be spited into the two sub web pages like each namesake will be at single web page. <s><br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> c).Name entity filtering: Some name entities are too ambiguous that name entities remove from this web page. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>4. Clustering: After performing the pre processing the web pages are clustered the clustering mechanism can follow the following steps. <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s>a).TF/IDF similarity: The Term Frequency and the Inverse Document Frequency can be calculated to identify the similarity of the name entities in the web page. The TF/IDF can be calculated as follows. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>For example there are 100 words in the document and 3 words are repeated the TF is calculated like 3/100=0.03 <br/> <s> <br/> <s>If there are 10000 documents and the word is repeated 100 times then IDF calculated as follows <s><br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> IDF = log(10000/100)=2. <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s>Now the TF/IDF is 2*0.03=0.06. <br/> <s> <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s>b).querying the web: Several co-occurrence queries are formed for the each pair of web pages d 1 and d 2 . These queries are given to the web search engine to get more information about the similarity. <br/> <s> <s> <s><br/> <s> <s> <s> <s>c).Making pair wise decision: After calculation of the co-occurrences we need to decide which pages are similar to the each other for this there will be one mechanism called skyline based approach. This approach is based on the TF/IDF similarity the output of the skyline based approach is directly aggregated with direct feature <br/> <s>similarity to compute the overall similarity of the web pages. <br/> <s> <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s>d).Applying clustering: There are two types of clustering can be perform either single link clustering or correlation clustering can be performed with output of skyline based classification web pages. The clustering is <br/> <s>nothing but combining the web pages this clustering procedure can be explained clearly. <br/> <s> <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s>e).Post processing: In the post processing step the data can segmented and filtered and finally the post processing steps are as follows <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s>1. Cluster sketches are computed based on skyline classification output. <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s>2. Each cluster rank is computed based on the two approaches one is web search engine ordering web pages and other one is keywords of context entities.'),
(48, '<img src="uploads/rahul/projectPic/2015-01-13_04:38:44am_UX-infographic.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/> The origins and meaning of â€œUser Experience / UX Designâ€ may seem a bit murky at first glance, to many not already familiar with it. One early use of it, without â€œuserâ€ prefixed, appeared in the nascent â€œAdvance for Designâ€ meetings organized by Clement Mok et al, under AIGA sponsorship, between 1998 and 2000. Mention is made, too, in the first post to uxmatters.com, of Don Norman using the term at Apple as early as 1993. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Though implying a Gestalt approach to interactive media design, that is, using a collection of elements to form a pattern which is greater than the sum of its parts, UX Design also puts special emphasis on the human side of human-computer interaction, and its affective results, rather than on the mere usabilityâ€”the human performance aspectâ€”of computer interface design, which traditionally relates to the field of ergonomics. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Usability is of course one of the primary concerns of the user-centric web designer, so it is easy to see how these related areas overlap, and lead to confusion, especially when no dictionary entry exists for UX Design (that Iâ€™ve seen), and people often use novel terms in various ways before understanding them well. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Another dimension of UX Design, as it related to the field of web design, is the historical one. As professional web design has evolved, and roles and responsibilities have advanced and divided, the professional web design community has had to find ways to differentiate itself from so many entering the field as amateurs, claiming the Web Designer moniker, and as web software programs began to democratize web production. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Ref: http://uxdesign.com/about-user-experience-design/article/what-is-ux/4');
