(128, '<img src="uploads/rahul/projectPic/2015-01-23_09:39:32am_7cfb66c9-d0e6-4d6d-85ea-619d45233375-620x372.jpeg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/> Field of the Invention: <br/> <s> <br/> <s>The present invention relates to a system for remotely tracking the location of an object using Bluetooth technology. <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Background of Invention: <br/> <s>It is an age old problem of keeping things and forgetting where it was kept. We often lose or misplace frequently used objects. Objects of immediate and great importance when lost or misplaced can cause great mental agony and inconvenience. This problem can now be overcome using trackers which determine the location of the object which has been tagged with such a tracker. <s><br/> <s> <br/> <s>Using such location tracking devices, important objects which we tend to frequently misplace such as TV remote controls, keys to our various locks etc. can be tagged. Even pet animals and children can be tagged and tracked. <s><br/> <s>The variety of existing devices are either too bulky or too expensive or have provide too little battery backup to be practical and effective. The invention in the instant case provides an alternative and addresses most of the aforementioned problems to give the user a practical solution to the age old problem. The existing GPS based tracking devices offer lower levels of accuracy which may not be sufficient to locate smaller portable objects such as keys etc. GPS based tracking devices are dependent on weather conditions and have limited functionality cloudy or storm like climate prevails. <s>The present invention overcomes all such shortcomings and gives a more reliable and simplified user experience. <s> <br/> <s> <br/> <s>Objects of the Invention: <br/> <s> <br/> <s>The objectives of the invention comprise of the following primary objects among other. <br/> <s> a) To provide facility of tagging personnel or portable objects. <br/> <s> b) To provide facility to track the location of such personnel or portable object. <s><br/> <s> c) To provide functionality of displaying the location to the user over a device such as a mobile phone or a computer or such device. <br/> <s> d) To facilitate the user in tracking down the personnel or object by giving directions to reach such location. <s><br/> <s> e) To allow for efficient use of battery so that the life on single charge can be extended by a substantial period of time.'),
