(40, 30, 296, 0, 'What is the number of elements that are compared to k, in the worst case?', 'A 2-d array of size nxn is given with the following property: Â  <br/> <s>Â Â all rows and columns are in ascending sorted order. Â  <br/> <s>Â  <br/> <s>To find a given element k in the array, this procedure is given: Â  <br/> <s>Â Â  Â  <br/> <s>Â  1. Start at top right element Â  <br/> <s>Â  2. For current element e Â  <br/> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s>1. if e = k Â  <br/> <s>Â Â  <s> <s> <s> <s> <s> <s>1. return true Â  <br/> <s>Â  <s> <s> <s> 2. if k <a>lt; element e Â  <br/> <s>Â Â 	 <s> <s> <s> 1. move to left, if possible. If array<r>s left bound reached, quit. Â  <br/> <s>Â Â  <s> <s> <s>3. if k <a>gt; element e Â  <br/> <s>Â Â 	 <s> <s> <s> 1. move to bottom, if possible. If array<r>s bottom bound reached, quit.	 Â  <br/> <s>Â Â  Â  <br/> <s>Â Â What is the number of elements that are compared to k, in the worst case? Â  <br/> <s>Â Â For more interview questions, stay in touch at http://collap.com/project.php?project_id=30', 1, '2015-01-20 06:30:46', 999999, 1, 1, '2015-01-20 06:34:51'),
