(40, 0, 469, 0, 'Solveit, Galliv-Ant up the Pyramid: A Geometry problem.', '<img src="uploads/shruti/challengePic/2015-02-02_11:11:26am_pyramid_png.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;" onError="this.src="img/default.gif"" /><br/> A right pyramid is having a square base ABCD of length 2 units. Its apex point E is such that the vertical height is 1 unit. An ant climbs up the surface from the point on the base A to the mid-point of slanted edge CE taking the shortest route. Â  <br/> <s>Â If the square of the distance traversed by the ant is given by a proper ratio m/n, <s><br/> <s>Â then what would be addition of m, <s>n ?', 1, '2015-02-02 11:11:26', 999999, 3, 1, '2015-02-02 11:13:06'),
