(7, 30, 766, 0, 'Find the latency of retrieving a cache block starting at address zero from main memory ??', ' <s>A CPU has a cache with block size 64 bytes. Â  <br/> <s> Â The main memory has k banks, each bank being c bytes wide. Â  <br/> <s> Â Consecutive câˆ’byte chunks are mapped on consecutive banks with wrap-around. Â  <br/> <s> Â All the k banks can be accessed in parallel, but two accesses to the same bank must be serialized. Â  <br/> <s> Â A cache block access may involve multiple iterations of parallel bank accesses depending on the amount of data obtained by accessing all the k banks in parallel. Â  <br/> <s> Â Each iteration requires decoding the bank numbers to be accessed in parallel and this takes k/2 ns . <s><br/> <s> Â The latency of one bank access is 80 ns. Â  <br/> <s> Â If c = 2 and k = 24, the latency of retrieving a cache block starting at address zero from main memory is: Â  <br/> <s> Â (A) 92 ns <s><br/> <s> Â (B) 104 ns <s><br/> <s> Â (C) 172 ns Â  <br/> <s> Â (D) 184 ns', 1, '2015-02-22 06:15:47', 999999, 1, 1, '2015-02-22 06:16:52'),
(7, 30, 767, 0, 'Find the total execution time of the program??', ' CPU has a five-stage pipeline and runs at 1 GHz frequency. <s><br/> <s>Instruction fetch happens in the first stage of the pipeline. <s><br/> <s>A conditional branch instruction computes the target address and evaluates the condition in the third stage of the pipeline. <s><br/> <s>The processor stops fetching new instructions following a conditional branch until the branch outcome is known. <s><br/> <s>A program executes 10^9 instructions out of which 20% are conditional branches. <s><br/> <s>If each instruction takes one cycle to complete on average, <s><br/> <s>the total execution time of the program is: <s><br/> <s>(A) 1.0 second <br/> <s>(B) 1.2 seconds <br/> <s>(C) 1.4 seconds <br/> <s>(D) 1.6 seconds <s>', 1, '2015-02-22 06:20:45', 999999, 1, 1, '2015-02-22 06:20:44'),
