(7, 2, 815, 0, 'Find the speed of the gear ??', 'The speed of a gear having 60 teeth is measured using a proximity sensor. <s><br/> <s>The output of the proximity sensor is fed to a counter with a gating time of 1s. <s><br/> <s>The counter indicates a value of 120. <s><br/> <s> <br/> <s>The speed at which the gear is rotating is <br/> <s>(A) 60 rpm <br/> <s>(B) 120 rpm <br/> <s>(C) 600 rpm <br/> <s>(D) 1200 rpm', 1, '2015-02-24 09:16:23', 999999, 1, 1, '2015-02-24 09:16:22'),
